WEBVTT

00:02.502 --> 00:06.256
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:06.256 --> 00:09.092
MAN (on TV): ...so grab your rod
and reel, and join us next week

00:09.092 --> 00:13.596
when Jim takes us trolling
on Lake Winnebeshaki.

00:13.596 --> 00:16.015
Nice show, huh?

00:16.015 --> 00:18.518
Well, if you ask me,
there's something wrong

00:18.518 --> 00:20.520
with watching televised fishing.

00:20.520 --> 00:21.905
Not the same impact

00:21.905 --> 00:24.157
as watching it live, huh, Woody?

00:24.157 --> 00:25.492
Hey, you know something?

00:25.492 --> 00:26.493
I got a great idea.

00:26.493 --> 00:27.994
What's to stop us

00:27.994 --> 00:30.246
from taking a little
fishing trip ourselves?

00:30.246 --> 00:31.581
We don't want to?

00:31.581 --> 00:32.582
Oh.

00:32.582 --> 00:33.583
Come on, it'd be fun.

00:33.583 --> 00:34.451
You know, we could go

00:34.451 --> 00:35.835
this very afternoon,

00:35.835 --> 00:37.337
head out to Lake Winthrop, huh?

00:37.337 --> 00:39.205
What do you say? NORM: All right.

00:39.205 --> 00:41.124
Okay. All right, let's get
organized here, uh, Woody.

00:41.124 --> 00:42.625
Uh, I'd like you to be in charge

00:42.625 --> 00:43.626
of bait and tackle, okay?

00:43.626 --> 00:44.627
Got you.

00:44.627 --> 00:45.628
Cliffy in charge of, uh,

00:45.628 --> 00:46.629
food and the transportation.

00:46.629 --> 00:47.630
Okay.

00:47.630 --> 00:49.516
Well, what're you in
charge of, Mr. Peterson?

00:49.516 --> 00:50.800
Finding a reason not to go.

00:52.302 --> 00:53.553
Ah, here we go.

00:53.553 --> 00:55.855
Huh? Gladiator film
festival at the Majestic.

00:55.855 --> 00:56.856
CLIFF: Yeah, that's a good one.

00:56.856 --> 00:58.725
? Boom, boom, boom, boom ?

00:58.725 --> 00:59.976
(humming dramatic fanfare)

00:59.976 --> 01:02.979
De gustibus non est disputandum!

01:02.979 --> 01:05.865
(humming continues)

01:08.785 --> 01:12.622
(piano plays)

01:12.622 --> 01:15.075
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:15.075 --> 01:18.078
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:18.078 --> 01:21.081
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:21.081 --> 01:24.084
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:24.084 --> 01:29.472
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:29.472 --> 01:32.258
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:32.258 --> 01:37.263
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:37.263 --> 01:42.268
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:42.268 --> 01:44.270
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:44.270 --> 01:47.273
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:47.273 --> 01:52.278
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:52.278 --> 01:55.281
? You want to go where people know ?

01:55.281 --> 01:57.283
? People are all the same ?

